<section class="alert-panel">
    <h2>Project Purpose</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Built a small Blazor/.NET demo project for an IoT Programmer interview.</li>
        <li>The app is themed around the TARDIS from Doctor Who.</li>
        <li>The actual structure is based on an industrial IoT monitoring dashboard.</li>
        <li>It simulates equipment and sensor telemetry, evaluates readings, and displays system status and alerts.</li>
        <li>The goal was to demonstrate Blazor fundamentals, C#/.NET skills, component-based UI, routing, services, dependency injection, and dashboard-style data visualization.</li>
    </ul>
</section>

