<section class="alert-panel">
    <h2>Telemetry Logic Added</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Each subsystem has simulated readings.</li>
        <li>Each reading has a value, unit, warning threshold, and critical threshold.</li>
        <li><code>SimulateTelemetryUpdate</code> randomly changes the readings.</li>
        <li>The app checks readings against thresholds.</li>
        <li>If a value is normal, the system status is Stable.</li>
        <li>If a value reaches the warning threshold, the system status becomes Warning.</li>
        <li>If a value reaches the critical threshold, the system status becomes Critical.</li>
        <li>Warning alerts are generated for warning-level readings.</li>
        <li>Critical alerts are generated for critical-level readings.</li>
    </ul>
</section>

